In a message dated 9/7/05 10:57:50 AM, learning_is_fun@... writes:


> -=-Didn't know there was a conference coming up. Where? When?-=-
>
http://www.liveandlearnconference.org/

October 6-9, near St. Louis

If you're interested, go that site and read all about it.

The conferences before this were in:
South Carolina 2002
South Carolina 2003 (because Kelly Lovejoy, the organizer, lives there)
Massachusetts 2004
and might, in 2006, be in New Mexico.

Sandra

messages.messageBody:
How do I get a mentor?
Lordy mercy I NEED one?
Tricia

Jill Parmer <jparmer@...> wrote:
30 days to the conference! ::::hailing all:::: Get your mentors, get your mentors now. A real live person you can talk to at the conference about your particular unschooling questions! ;-)

Need more mentors, too. Please consider, if you haven't signed up to be one.

Have fun,
Jill
